# UXCraft opt-in trigger

When the user writes `/uxcraft`, activate the installed UXCraft workflow. Do not use it automatically without the trigger.

Follow `.uxcraft/SKILL.md` first, with installed-package fallback. Check UI/UX memory first, preserve existing brand/tokens/components, and include accessibility, responsive behavior, states, content, quality gates, and implementation handoff.
